reviews.reviewText: So i got to try this for free with crowdtap, and its amazing it makes my coffee so super yummy i wanna drink cup after cup <3

reviews.name: Folgers Flavors Hazelnut Coffee Enhancer, 1.62 fl oz
reviews.reviewText: It shouldn't take more than three squirts to flavor a cup of coffee. I had to double that to taste the hazelnut flavor at all. Definitely not enough bang for my buck.
reviews.title: Not Impressed

reviews.name: Folgers Flavors Hazelnut Coffee Enhancer, 1.62 fl oz
reviews.reviewText: I decided to try this as a way to enjoy flavor in my iced coffee and was surprised how much flavor it adds! Best part is that it has no calories or carbs!! I'll gladly try them all and hope you will, too.
reviews.title: GREAT PRODUCT!!!!!!!
